    "description": "Our hero Themhem and his lost love Ale met a few years ago and fell in love in first sight. There have been times that their love faltered but somehow they always managed to stay together and happy. Nevertheless by a twist of fate an evil soul  cursed Themhem and locked him in a dungeon. Themhem now has to defeat endless deadly enemies in dungeons to reach the love of his life; Ale. However, the further he goes, the longer it takes to reach her. In the meantime, Ale, who is oblivious of Themhem's curse, makes various requests from Themhem. Of course our tireless hero tries his best to fulfill her wishes with all his might.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158870/extras/e21229ee6d8dc3708bd51a4b0439d477.webp?t=1673995697\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158870/extras/e5516bcb0fe6603f335bbcf85f71d9ce.poster.avif?t=1673995697\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158870/extras/e5516bcb0fe6603f335bbcf85f71d9ce.webm?t=1673995697\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158870/extras/e5516bcb0fe6603f335bbcf85f71d9ce.mp4?t=1673995697\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158870/extras/e21229ee6d8dc3708bd51a4b0439d477.webp?t=1673995697\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br><br>2d top-down adventure game. Destroy the enemies that come upon you with the weapons you collect. Advance through levels by solving puzzles and meet Ale.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158870/extras/e21229ee6d8dc3708bd51a4b0439d477.webp?t=1673995697\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br><br>Do not forget to open the Chests and boxes around you. There will be gifts for you. You can also find a few items that will make it easier for you to meet with Ale.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158870/extras/e21229ee6d8dc3708bd51a4b0439d477.webp?t=1673995697\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158870/extras/b0eba54741380d3302712a8fee26dc7f.poster.avif?t=1673995697\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158870/extras/b0eba54741380d3302712a8fee26dc7f.webm?t=1673995697\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158870/extras/b0eba54741380d3302712a8fee26dc7f.mp4?t=1673995697\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158870/extras/e21229ee6d8dc3708bd51a4b0439d477.webp?t=1673995697\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br><br>The chapters progress in the form of rooms and there are more than 100 chapters in total. To meet Ale, you need to find the keys to the doors and pass their sections. But watch out for the enemies. They may hurt you, but we don't know if they hurt as much as Ale...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158870/extras/e21229ee6d8dc3708bd51a4b0439d477.webp?t=1673995697\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamst